{"type":"USJ","version":"3.1","content":[{"type":"book","marker":"id","content":["63-2JN-web.sfm English Arabic Names Version (EANV)"],"code":"2JN"},{"type":"para","marker":"ide","content":["UTF-8\n"]},{"type":"para","marker":"h","content":["2 Yuhanna \n"]},{"type":"para","marker":"toc1","content":["Yuhanna’s Second Letter \n"]},{"type":"para","marker":"toc2","content":["2 Yuhanna \n"]},{"type":"para","marker":"toc3","content":["2Jn \n"]},{"type":"para","marker":"mt1","content":["Yuhanna’s Second Letter \n"]},{"type":"chapter","marker":"c","number":"1","sid":"2JN 1"},{"type":"para","marker":"p","content":[{"type":"verse","marker":"v","number":"1","sid":"2JN 1:1"},"The elder, to the chosen lady and her children, whom I love in truth, and not I only, but also all those who know the\ntruth, \n",{"type":"verse","marker":"v","number":"2","sid":"2JN 1:2"},"for the truth’s sake, which remains in us, and it will be with us forever:\n",{"type":"verse","marker":"v","number":"3","sid":"2JN 1:3"},"Grace, mercy, and peace will be with us, from Allah the Father, and from the Lord Al Masih Isa, the Son of the Father, in\ntruth and love. \n"]},{"type":"para","marker":"p","content":[{"type":"verse","marker":"v","number":"4","sid":"2JN 1:4"},"I rejoice greatly that I have found some of your children walking in truth, even as we have been commanded by the Father.\n",{"type":"verse","marker":"v","number":"5","sid":"2JN 1:5"},"Now I beg you, dear lady, not as though I wrote to you a new commandment, but that which we had from the beginning, that\nwe love one another. \n",{"type":"verse","marker":"v","number":"6","sid":"2JN 1:6"},"This is love, that we should walk according to his commandments. This is the commandment, even as you heard from the\nbeginning, that you should walk in it. \n",{"type":"verse","marker":"v","number":"7","sid":"2JN 1:7"},"For many deceivers have gone out into the world, those who don’t confess that Al Masih Isa came in the flesh. This is the\ndeceiver and the Antichrist. \n",{"type":"verse","marker":"v","number":"8","sid":"2JN 1:8"},"Watch yourselves, that we don’t lose the things which we have accomplished, but that we receive a full reward.\n",{"type":"verse","marker":"v","number":"9","sid":"2JN 1:9"},"Whoever transgresses and doesn’t remain in the teaching of Masih, doesn’t have Allah. He who remains in the teaching has\nboth the Father and the Son. \n",{"type":"verse","marker":"v","number":"10","sid":"2JN 1:10"},"If anyone comes to you, and doesn’t bring this teaching, don’t receive him into your house, and don’t welcome him,\n",{"type":"verse","marker":"v","number":"11","sid":"2JN 1:11"},"for he who welcomes him participates in his evil deeds. \n"]},{"type":"para","marker":"p","content":[{"type":"verse","marker":"v","number":"12","sid":"2JN 1:12"},"Having many things to write to you, I don’t want to do so with paper and ink, but I hope to come to you, and to speak\nface to face, that our joy may be made full. \n",{"type":"verse","marker":"v","number":"13","sid":"2JN 1:13"},"The children of your chosen sister greet you. Amen. "]}]}